      "rationale": "Three-level mesh refinement study conducted with refinement ratio r = 1.5. GCI on NIH < 2.1% and on peak wall shear stress < 3.8%. Richardson extrapolation applied; asymptotic range confirmed (GCI_fine/GCI_coarse ≈ 1.02). Exceeds Gradation 2 requirement.",
