      "rationale": "In-vitro test conditions (blood analog fluid, rotational speed, inlet flow waveform) matched to CFD boundary conditions. Temperature controlled at 37°C ± 0.5°C; fluid viscosity measured before each run. Deviations from nominal documented and propagated into uncertainty budget.",
