      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "rationale": "NIH and relative hemolysis index (RH) are the primary regulatory QoIs for blood pump hemolysis assessment per FDA guidance. Scalar shear stress exposure time (SET) used as intermediate QoI linking CFD flow field to blood damage model. Mapping from CFD outputs to regulatory QoIs documented.",
