      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "rationale": "Validation experiments performed on the same FDA generic centrifugal blood pump geometry at the same five operating points as the COU. Blood analog fluid (glycerol-water) viscosity matched to whole blood at 37°C. Geometric fidelity confirmed via CMM measurement of test article.",
