      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorStatus": "scoped-out",
      "rationale": "Numerical solver error is scoped out at MRL 2 for this COU. The commercial solver (ANSYS Fluent) carries independent V&V documentation covering iterative convergence and round-off error for rotating machinery flows. Residual convergence to 1e-6 on all equations confirmed for every operating point; iterative error contribution to NIH estimated < 0.5% via Richardson extrapolation on iteration count."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
