      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorStatus": "scoped-out",
      "rationale": "Test samples factor is scoped out at MRL 2. Five independent experimental replicates were used; sample-to-sample variability in NIH was 6.2% (CV), within the expected biological variability for blood analog experiments. No additional sample characterization is required at this model risk level."
